N rddensity.pkg
D 30 Apr 2026
U 3
d 'RDDENSITY': module to perform  Manipulation Testing Using Local Polynomial Density Estimation
d 
d   rddensity implements manipulation testing procedures using the
d local polynomial density estimators proposed       in Cattaneo,
d Jansson and Ma (2020), and implements graphical procedures with
d valid confidence bands using       the results in Cattaneo,
d Jansson and Ma (2021).  In addition, the command provides
d complementary        manipulation testing based on finite sample
d exact binomial testing following the results in Cattaneo,
d Frandsen and Titiunik (2015) and Cattaneo, Frandsen and
d Vazquez-Bare (2017). For an introduction to       manipulation
d testing see McCrary (2008).
d 
d KW: manipulation
d KW: local polynomial density
d 
d Requires: Stata version 14 and lpdensity from SSC (q.v.)
d 
d Distribution-Date: 20220708
d 
d Author: Matias D. Cattaneo, Department of Operations Research and Financial Engineering, Princeton University
d Support: email cattaneo@@princeton.edu
d 
d Author: Michael Jansson, Department of Economics, UC-Berkeley
d Support: email mjansson@@econ.berkeley.edu
d 
d Author:  Xinwei Ma, Department of Economics, UCSD
d Support: email x1ma@@ucsd.edu
d 
f r\rdbwdensity.ado
f r\rdbwdensity.sthlp
f r\rddensity.ado
f r\rddensity.sthlp
f r\rddensity_fv.mo
f r\rddensity_h.mo
f r\rddensity_quantile.mo
f r\rddensity_rep.mo
f r\rddensity_unique.mo
e
