N lpdensity.pkg
D 30 Apr 2026
U 10
d 'LPDENSITY': module to perform Local Polynomial Density Estimation and Inference
d 
d   lpdensity implements the local polynomial regression based
d density (and derivatives) estimator proposed in  Cattaneo,
d Jansson and Ma (2020).  Robust bias-corrected inference, both
d pointwise (confidence intervals)   and uniform (confidence
d bands) are also implemented following the results in Cattaneo,
d Jansson and Ma (2020) and Cattaneo, Jansson and Ma
d (2022a).  See Cattaneo, Jansson and Ma (2022b) for more
d implementation details and illustrations.
d 
d KW: local polynomial
d KW: density
d KW: bias-corrected inference
d 
d Requires: Stata version 14
d 
d Distribution-Date: 20220708
d 
d Author: Matias D. Cattaneo, Department of Operations Research and Financial Engineering, Princeton University
d Support: email cattaneo@@princeton.edu
d 
d Author: Michael Jansson, Department of Economics, UC-Berkeley
d Support: email mjansson@@econ.berkeley.edu
d 
d Author:  Xinwei Ma, Department of Economics, UCSD
d Support: email x1ma@@ucsd.edu
d 
